      <description><![CDATA[
<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li><b>Auto-updates via Sparkle.</b> This build checks the release feed automatically — updates arrive on their own, EdDSA-signed and notarized.</li>
<li><b>Settings → Updates</b> now shows the app version and build number.</li>
</ul>
